snippet.title: Prince Harry Was Warned About Meghan Markle. Here's Why.
snippet.description:
The tell-all book Royals at War: The Untold Story of Harry and Meghan’s Shocking Split with The House of Windsor has been released and it gives a detailed account of the Duke and Duchess of Sussex's split from the royal family.

The explosive expose doesn’t just give readers details of what the press is calling Megxit, but it also shares info about the warning signs the royals gave Prince Harry before he made the decision to tie the knot with his now-wife.

This is not the first time the British royals have been opposed to a controversial American woman and here is why they warned Prince Harry this time.

#PrinceHarry #MeghanMarkle #RoyalFamily

Read Full Article: https://www.thelist.com/222769/the-reason-prince-harry-was-warned-about-meghan-markle/
